<h3 class="date"><a href="/2010/sep/27/">&#x27a0;</a> September 27, 2010</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="cloudflare" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="https://www.cloudflare.com/">CloudFlare</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Crazy smart security and caching system for websites. You repoint your domain&#8217;s DNS to their servers, and everything gets cached and filtered automagically.  Comment spam has almost entirely disappeared since I installed it on my blog.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
