        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/259425">US-CERT: Adobe Flash vulnerability</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>All current versions of Flash Player are remotely exploitable on all platforms.  &#8220;This vulnerability is being actively exploited.&#8221;  Only workaround is to uninstall Flash Player.</p>

