<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/jan/05/">&#x27a0;</a> January 5, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Obama Phished?</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/3171319990/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Obama Phished?" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1044/3171319990_d5a0d5f90f_m.jpg" height="113" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Looks like the president-elect's Twitter credentials <a href="https://twitter.com/BarackObama/status/1097508218">have been compromised</a>.</p>
        </p>

