<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/dec/30/">&#x27a0;</a> December 30, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="md5-considered-harmful-today" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.win.tue.nl/hashclash/rogue-ca/">MD5 considered harmful today</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>MD5 collisions can be used to make SSL certificates that modern browsers will trust for any domain.  This is a: Bad Thing.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
